ts-frontman-milo-aukerman-suffers-mild-heart-attack-3475256">《后裔》主唱米洛·奥克曼 (Milo Aukerman) 患有“轻度心脏病”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
